Direct Rendering Manager (DRM) modules for LinuxKPI-based kernel mode setting
(KMS) components. Modules for amdgpu, i915, and radeon. This metaport
encompasses recommended versions of DRM, based on the most recent updates to
the LinuxKPI in specific versions of FreeBSD.

Installing this metaport will – additionally – install the port of the most
recent supported stable modules for the running version of FreeBSD.
